params.postRoot: The root obtained after deleting all of `identityCommitments` into the tree        described by `preRoot`. Must be an element of the field `Kr`.
params.preRoot: The value for the root of the tree before the corresponding identity commitments have been deleted. Must be an element of the field `Kr`.

params.identityCommitments: The identities that were inserted into the tree starting at        `startIndex` and `preRoot` to give `postRoot`. All of the commitments must be        elements of the field `Kr`.
params.postRoot: The root obtained after inserting all of `identityCommitments` into the tree        described by `preRoot`. Must be an element of the field `Kr`. (alread in reduced form)
params.startIndex: The position in the tree at which the insertions were made.
